---
title: Sesame Coated Salmon  with zesty rice and broccoli
description: This sesame sprinkled salmon is smothered in a tangy and slightly spicy Asian-inspired sauce. Zesty rice and perfectly charred broccoli round out a truly moreish meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R11_W29_IE_IEXCF15671-2_less_bright_edit_Main_high-a1fb2950.jpg
